{"tid":883061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀亞士厘道間京笹居酒屋都幾仆街","createTime":"2018-10-30T14:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T05:55:43.000Z","uid":142484,"like":16,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"73e74b6707eb8aac86d07721381e3934aafc472a","tid":883061,"uid":142484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:04:55.000Z","msg":"話說同女友去試下新餐廳  一坐底就擺低個豆腐乾前菜 一人一碟 咩都冇講過<br />\n<br />\n本身都覺得唔錯 環境食物都幾好 點知一埋單見到個前菜收左$46 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  問佢個侍應 又er....唔回應 問佢經理又笑笑口咁話我地不嬲張張枱都係咁收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘈多兩句都知冇轉變 屌多兩句就轉身走 <br />\n<br />\n講真$46唔係俾唔起 但我會選擇用依$46去叫另一碟菜 你咁樣同呃人有咩分別？好一間不知所謂既餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/220439_61fc573ee83ba84c5894d877b8752aca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F220439_61fc573ee83ba84c5894d877b8752aca.png&h=d7b2502e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/220441_fbcf643034fe3f7c1a322e69407c2e48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F220441_fbcf643034fe3f7c1a322e69407c2e48.png&h=94b6f9e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20ffbb8131a4638b9f844ba57bdae3a2a85b296e","tid":883061,"uid":158755,"like":44,"dislike":4,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"日本居酒屋有前菜就一定要收錢<br />\n同埋唔會同你講，呢樣就真係慣例<br />\n佢開喺香港都抄埋呢套啫"},{"pid":"3974e5bf60e67efdb1c30a44a36caf0b35d660f5","tid":883061,"uid":86717,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"學生？前菜要比錢有咩出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食隻溫泉蛋80蚊隻你都要比"},{"pid":"296c515832d8c53f2fc527416eb0fe97bd324e04","tid":883061,"uid":7568