喇<br />\n抵比46蚊收平左"},{"pid":"cc3a53f8bddc746e5025ee82792b146c0eaea5d1","tid":883061,"uid":76747,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"在日本居酒屋用餐，點第一杯酒時同時會送上一小盤小，日文叫作「お通し」，主要是讓客人在等待上餐前可以享用的一種小菜，配上酒品絕搭，通常也是你不用點餐也會送上桌唷，有些店是免費，有些店則是要收費，可是日本人飲酒前的一個重要文化唷。<br />\n<br />\n下次食日本野睇撚清楚啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地笑你無知咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6087048fa2b45c3daceb33d9bac8de82f7d445","tid":883061,"uid":17616,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"其實呢個前菜係要硬食，日本都係咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過</span></span><br />\n人地日本係無收加一，而睇返樓主張單最後個?????料似係加一，<br />\n呢間鋪收晒兩地著數係唔抵幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc932fa304522d4d147228e38e4e9459bda193e","tid":883061,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"733d8b944152fca66eeb255f2363d5875678a753","tid":883061,"uid":142484,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"27578dc486afab1d7add118f4764d36dfa8b278c","tid":883061,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"61bf7eb6d8aa00d5ce6a85c2b853bf11ef8c35e1","tid":883061,"uid":142484,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"茶錢係香港人都知有 <br />\n日本居酒屋前菜會唔會問都唔問就擺低收$46？<br />\n <br />\n同埋唔係個個都知日本居酒屋前菜要收錢<br />\n既然你開係香港 會唔會放低前解釋下好d?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"當中式酒樓前菜食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你宜家下次咪知囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"咁你下次去餐廳飲水佢收你$200 記得咪出聲 <br />\n唔係又俾人笑你俾唔起